## 三、问题总览与分析

### 3.1 问题数量统计

| 问题分类 | 数量 | 占比 |
|----------|------|------|
| **覆盖问题总数** | **{{ overview.problem_count or 0 }}** | **100%** |
| 低小聚类-楼宇问题 | {{ overview.problem_build_dj_count or 0 }} | {{ "%.1f"|format(((overview.problem_build_dj_count or 0) / (overview.problem_count or 1) * 100) if (overview.problem_count or 0) > 0 else 0) }}% |
| 高大单点-楼宇问题 | {{ overview.problem_build_d_count or 0 }} | {{ "%.1f"|format(((overview.problem_build_d_count or 0) / (overview.problem_count or 1) * 100) if (overview.problem_count or 0) > 0 else 0) }}% |
| 质差劣于竞对-楼宇 | {{ overview.problem_bad_other_count or 0 }} | {{ "%.1f"|format(((overview.problem_bad_other_count or 0) / (overview.problem_count or 1) * 100) if (overview.problem_count or 0) > 0 else 0) }}% |
| 4G栅格MDT问题 | {{ overview.problem_grid_4g_count or 0 }} | {{ "%.1f"|format(((overview.problem_grid_4g_count or 0) / (overview.problem_count or 1) * 100) if (overview.problem_count or 0) > 0 else 0) }}% |
| 5G栅格云瞰问题 | {{ overview.problem_grid_5g_count or 0 }} | {{ "%.1f"|format(((overview.problem_grid_5g_count or 0) / (overview.problem_count or 1) * 100) if (overview.problem_count or 0) > 0 else 0) }}% |
| **其他问题** | | |
| 干扰问题 | {{ overview.gr_problem_count or 0 }} | - |
| 结构问题 | {{ overview.jg_problem_count or 0 }} | - |
| 维护问题 | {{ overview.wh_problem_count or 0 }} | - |

### 3.2 问题严重程度评估

{% set total_problems = (overview.problem_count or 0) + (overview.gr_problem_count or 0) + (overview.jg_problem_count or 0) + (overview.wh_problem_count or 0) %}
{% if total_problems > 100 %}
🔴 **严重**: 发现 {{ total_problems }} 个问题，需要立即采取行动
{% elif total_problems > 50 %}
🟡 **中等**: 发现 {{ total_problems }} 个问题，建议尽快处理
{% elif total_problems > 0 %}
🟢 **轻微**: 发现 {{ total_problems }} 个问题，可按计划优化
{% else %}
✅ **良好**: 未发现明显问题
{% endif %}

{% if (overview.problem_bad_other_count or 0) > 0 %}
⚠️ **重点关注**: 发现 **{{ overview.problem_bad_other_count }}** 个劣于竞对的楼宇，占覆盖问题的 **{{ "%.1f"|format(((overview.problem_bad_other_count or 0) / (overview.problem_count or 1) * 100) if (overview.problem_count or 0) > 0 else 0) }}%**，需优先解决。
{% endif %}

